Text:
Classification: Documentary
Genre: Pets/Animals
Status: New Series
Network: ITV ( United Kingdom)
Airs: Thursdays at 09:00 pm
Runtime: 60 Minutes
Premiere: January 31, 2013

Secret Life of Dogs is a documentary narrated by Martin Clunes. Scientists have taken a look into the canine mind and body and the results are mind-blowing as the show discovers the truth behind dogs’ super powers, their undying loyalty and the incredible intuition of being man’s best friend.
